============================================================

All good. The improvement plan has already been fully implemented in the working tree. Here's what was done:

**All 8 changes from the plan are implemented:**

1. **OCR Normalization** — `normalizeOcrTitle()` + `toTitleCase()` functions added; called on every return path at line 1130
2. **Page/Section Filters** — `Page\s+\d+`, `Strona\s+\d+` filters in `passesHardFilters`; English category labels added to `SECTION_LABELS`; OCR variant (`lngredients` → `ingredients`) in `isSectionLabel`
3. **Overflow Detection** — `OVERFLOW_MARKERS` block in `findBurstEnd` skips previous-recipe preambles
4. **Compound Stripping Removed** — The `colonMatch` block that incorrectly truncated `LEMON CURD : LEMON CURD WITH THYME` is gone
5. **Multi-line Joining** — Hyphen-continuation pre-processing added; `placki` removed from `SECTION_LABELS`
6. **Annotation Filtering** — `[CORRUPTED SPILLOVER`, `(OCR\b`, `(.*\bcorruption\b` filters in `passesHardFilters`
7. **Colon Filter** — Lines ending with `:` (but not using ` : ` as title separator) are filtered in `passesHardFilters`
8. **Confidence Floor** — Fallback only triggers when `rawScore > 0.02`

**Tests: 33/33 passing. CLI: working.**
